{"tid":274133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指襲青關會成員判罰款　張達明助法輪功成員上訴得直","createTime":"2017-06-07T05:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T07:43:31.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12b68ff5a9bf9422cee725216544c78dc55b1115","tid":274133,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"法輪功成員詩曙明於前年4月在旺角惠豐中心外，與左派組織「香港青年關愛協會」(青關會)宣傳部主任張柳清因宣傳橫額問題起爭執，其間詩曙明被指大力拍打張柳清而被裁定普通襲擊罪成判罰。香港大學法律學院首席講師張達明早前代表詩向高院提上訴，法官今頒下判詞，指有新證據顯示張針對法輸功，終裁定詩上訴得直，撤銷定罪。<br />\n<br />\n法官在判詞指投訴人張柳清在過去34個月內牽涉92宗報案紀錄，其中38宗張是報案人，有5宗涉及對法輪功的指控，包括糾紛、投訴滋擾、阻街等，其中一宗裁判官在審視張的證供時，曾批評張是故意針對法輪功，對法輪功存有不懷好意。法官指上述資料在原審時未有披露，而這些證據對張的可信性構成重大關係，故接納為上訴理據。<br />\n<br />\n另外張稱遭上訴人詩曙明拍打手臂，但根據張所拍攝的片段顯示，她當時是質問上訴人為何拍打其電話，而並沒就手臂受襲而質問上訴人，裁判官卻沒就此矛盾作出分析。辯方在原審時指張當時用手機近距離拍攝上訴人，上訴人對此感到厭惡，故用手輕撥張從而接觸到她的手臂，法官指此舉動不足以構成襲擊，在綜合新增的證據、以及原審裁判官對定罪分析的不足，撤銷上訴人的定罪。"},{"pid":"813dbc97cefd6c1e286409ddab8a245e84fd42c3","tid":274133,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56794993&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56794993%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170607&d=RqhwnB06MJQCJkBLgkiVqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=af8daa3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56794993%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170607&h=9dd0b978\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56794993&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170607</a>"},{"pid":"674c594cc3f6fd1dde80394b3bb7fc4f34e502e3","tid":274133,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:03:26.000Z","msg":"香港裁判官越黎越專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n杜浩成 陳碧橋都係我偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768dd2adede206b5158ce1c6bca0088980cfe7c5","tid":274133,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58481509418bd527e175c9fe111e8bcabedb7f9","tid":274133,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"法輸功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60d2eb6dfc7439d24076c95f5829037cb3d8141","tid":274133,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6269920941aed2f5300ee9ab3d1043f37ecbcdca","tid":274133,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"大紀元登頭版未?"},{"pid":"b4be68fdc2d44d3fe3592083432fdbf66e7f8b27","tid":274133,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T07:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}